imdb.plot outline: Emily Riedel returns with a brand new, state-of-the-art ice dredge. Facing major debt, she is out to prove that her success as Nome's first and only female dredge owner was not a fluke. Her father, Steve Riedel, is planning a comeback after losing his dredge to the repo man. The Pomrenkes are back too, following a record-setting summer, but having never succeeded under the ice.
